00:37:06,160 --> 00:37:07,680
Go back and finish your homework.

675
00:37:07,680 --> 00:37:07,970
Okay.

676
00:37:09,010 --> 00:37:11,050
Dad, I need to go home
and do my homework too.

677
00:37:11,050 --> 00:37:11,320
As if.

678
00:37:11,320 --> 00:37:13,160
You just want to head home
to play video games.

679
00:37:16,410 --> 00:37:17,610
Hello. Have a seat.

680
00:37:23,120 --> 00:37:24,280
Noodles for Table 2 are ready.

681
00:37:24,840 --> 00:37:25,640
Coming.

682
00:37:26,680 --> 00:37:27,720
You must be Qingyu.

683
00:37:30,890 --> 00:37:31,720
Who are you?

684
00:37:31,720 --> 00:37:33,410
How did you know about my sister's name?

685
00:37:34,050 --> 00:37:36,800
You're the son of He
from Nanqiao Village.

686
00:37:38,090 --> 00:37:38,890
Your name is...

687
00:37:39,280 --> 00:37:41,050
Mrs. Qiao, my name is He Feihai.

688
00:37:42,731 --> 00:37:45,220
(He Feihai's moves)

689
00:37:49,240 --> 00:37:50,360
I never expected you

690
00:37:50,360 --> 00:37:51,530
to come here today.

691
00:37:52,600 --> 00:37:54,160
I was attending university in Huanzhou.

692
00:37:54,440 --> 00:37:55,610
I just graduated not long ago.

693
00:37:55,880 --> 00:37:56,720
Thank you, Mrs. Qiao.

694
00:37:57,360 --> 00:37:59,320
Mr. Qiao, I heard from Jingrui

695
00:37:59,360 --> 00:38:01,130
that you guys opened a noodle shop
in Huanzhou.

696
00:38:01,440 --> 00:38:03,010
That's why I came here to check it out.

697
00:38:03,720 --> 00:38:04,530
I appreciate it.

698
00:38:05,450 --> 00:38:06,680
How are your parents doing?

699
00:38:06,760 --> 00:38:07,840
They're doing pretty good.

700
00:38:09,410 --> 00:38:10,840
Your parents are truly blessed.

701
00:38:10,960 --> 00:38:12,480
They managed to raise an undergraduate.

702
00:38:12,760 --> 00:38:14,720
It's worth it no matter
how tiring the process was.

703
00:38:15,450 --> 00:38:17,280
I'm way inferior compared to Jingrui.

704
00:38:20,490 --> 00:38:21,640
Mr. Qiao, Mrs. Qiao,

705
00:38:22,010 --> 00:38:23,130
actually, I came here

706
00:38:24,050 --> 00:38:25,010
because

707
00:38:26,280 --> 00:38:27,570
I thought you guys might not know

708
00:38:28,530 --> 00:38:30,890
that Beiyu and I were classmates.

709
00:38:30,890 --> 00:38:33,050
I only heard about
her passing not long ago.

710
00:38:33,680 --> 00:38:35,010
Please accept my condolences.

711
00:38:35,490 --> 00:38:38,970
What about this? Let's drop the past.

712
00:38:40,320 --> 00:38:41,760
Eat up.

713
00:38:41,760 --> 00:38:44,010
I prepared some simple dishes for you.

714
00:38:44,010 --> 00:38:47,010
But I followed the original recipe
from our hometown.

715
00:38:47,010 --> 00:38:48,090
You can't get it here.

716
00:38:48,890 --> 00:38:50,010
I remember now.

717
00:38:50,450 --> 00:38:53,490
He Feihai was once Jingrui's underling.

718
00:38:53,720 --> 00:38:55,610
He was always following Jingrui

719
00:38:55,610 --> 00:38:56,280
and Beiyu.

720
00:38:57,890 --> 00:38:59,760
Qiao Beiyu wrote in her diary

721
00:38:59,760 --> 00:39:01,760
that the person she loved the most
came to Huanzhou.

722
00:39:02,130 --> 00:39:04,200
He Feihai attended
university in Huanzhou.

723
00:39:05,320 --> 00:39:06,800
Could he be Qiao Beiyu's boyfriend,

724
00:39:06,800 --> 00:39:08,200
who was from Nanqiao Village?

725
00:39:10,890 --> 00:39:14,010
Don't tell me you're going
to cause trouble again.

726
00:39:14,490 --> 00:39:17,640
I don't want Mom
to be angry at me again.

727
00:39:18,530 --> 00:39:20,570
Don't worry.
I won't involve you this time.

728
00:39:21,320 --> 00:39:23,490
Go and get him some rice.

729
00:39:41,945 --> 00:39:46,870
(See you at the cafe next to
Huanzhou High School at 6 P.M. on Monday.)

730
00:39:48,360 --> 00:39:49,360
Come. Let me see you off.

731
00:39:49,360 --> 00:39:51,400
Mr. Qiao, it's fine.

732
00:39:51,530 --> 00:39:52,760
Your father and I

733
00:39:52,760 --> 00:39:54,280
grew up together.

734
00:39:54,560 --> 00:39:56,010
You don't need to stand on ceremony.

735
00:39:56,010 --> 00:39:58,480
In the future, just come to my shop
if you want to eat anything.

736
00:39:58,530 --> 00:40:00,050
Alright. Thank you, Mr. Qiao.

737
00:40:00,410 --> 00:40:03,400
Feihai, we made some
preserved vegetables.

738
00:40:03,400 --> 00:40:04,450
Please take them with you.

739
00:40:04,800 --> 00:40:06,760
I don't think this is appropriate.

740
00:40:06,760 --> 00:40:08,090
My wife made them. Just take them.

741
00:40:10,050 --> 00:40:10,720
Alright.

742
00:40:11,160 --> 00:40:13,610
Thank you, Qingyu and Mrs. Qiao.

743
00:40:13,760 --> 00:40:14,840
I'll head home first.

744
00:40:15,120 --> 00:40:16,280
I'll visit you guys next time.

745
00:40:17,570 --> 00:40:18,160
Take care.

746
00:40:35,840 --> 00:40:37,200
They were the champions last time.

747
00:40:38,480 --> 00:40:38,920
Let me see.

748
00:40:38,920 --> 00:40:40,050
What are you guys doing here?

749
00:40:40,120 --> 00:40:41,050
We registered our names.

