Basketball League)

751
00:40:42,970 --> 00:40:43,720
Four men, one team.

752
00:40:43,720 --> 00:40:45,040
Nope. We didn't participate in it.

753
00:40:45,240 --> 00:40:46,410
There's a basketball contest

754
00:40:46,410 --> 00:40:47,680
after school today.

755
00:40:47,880 --> 00:40:48,930
As the host of the contest,

756
00:40:49,200 --> 00:40:51,160
we have to cheer for

757
00:40:51,160 --> 00:40:52,360
our schoolmates.

758
00:40:52,410 --> 00:40:53,570
Okay!

759
00:40:55,520 --> 00:40:57,320
Qingyu, will you watch
the basketball match?

760
00:40:57,320 --> 00:40:58,090
Nope.

761
00:41:00,040 --> 00:41:01,490
Qiao Qingyu doesn't think of herself

762
00:41:01,490 --> 00:41:03,410
as a member of Class 5 at all.

763
00:41:03,760 --> 00:41:05,480
Yeah.

764
00:41:05,480 --> 00:41:06,970
Let's go. The match will start soon.

765
00:41:07,490 --> 00:41:08,360
Let's go.

766
00:41:22,640 --> 00:41:23,800
Please get me the menu.

767
00:41:26,130 --> 00:41:26,800
This is the menu.

768
00:41:26,800 --> 00:41:28,280
Please take a look.

769
00:41:30,610 --> 00:41:31,890
You asked me out today

770
00:41:32,440 --> 00:41:34,410
to inquire about what happened
to Qiao Beiyu, right?

