00:42:08,861 --> 00:42:11,081
♪Maybe♪

772
00:42:12,941 --> 00:42:18,341
♪The more I care,
the more I tread carefully♪

773
00:42:20,031 --> 00:42:25,381
♪Counting the distance between us♪

774
00:42:26,281 --> 00:42:32,541
♪Just one step away from reaching♪

775
00:42:37,541 --> 00:42:39,831
♪The future♪

776
00:42:41,531 --> 00:42:47,151
♪Time will unveil this mystery♪

777
00:42:48,731 --> 00:42:54,091
♪Waiting is a silent promise♪

778
00:42:54,941 --> 00:43:01,251
♪But one that never expires♪

779
00:43:03,571 --> 00:43:08,621
♪Turns out, all my thoughts♪

780
00:43:08,721 --> 00:43:13,031
♪Spell your name♪

781
00:43:13,321 --> 00:43:19,331
♪The one and only stubbornness
in my heart♪

782
00:43:19,551 --> 00:43:22,861
♪From the very first glance♪

783
00:43:23,211 --> 00:43:27,281
♪I started painting
what our future would look like♪

784
00:43:27,281 --> 00:43:33,551
♪That's when the dream began
to feel real♪

785
00:43:33,551 --> 00:43:37,211
♪Turns out♪

786
00:43:37,531 --> 00:43:41,591
♪Your heart had a place for me too♪

787
00:43:41,991 --> 00:43:47,971
♪Cradling the same story we both knew♪

788
00:43:48,241 --> 00:43:51,901
♪Thankfully, we were naïve enough♪

789
00:43:51,901 --> 00:43:55,441
♪And brave just in time♪

790
00:43:55,441 --> 00:44:02,421
♪To make sure our moments
weren't lost to time♪
